<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy — UniSpace</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --ink: #111118;
            --ink-soft: #5a5a6e;
            --ink-faint: #9898a8;
            --rule: rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
            --accent: #6366f1;
            --accent-soft: rgba(99,102,241,0.08);
            --bg: #fafaf9;
            --surface: #ffffff;
            --radius: 14px;
            --ease: cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
        }

        *, *::before, *::after { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }

        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--ink);
            min-height: 100vh;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        /* ── HOME BUTTON (fixed top-left) ── */
        .home-btn {
            position: fixed;
            top: 1.25rem;
            left: 1.25rem;
            z-index: 200;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.4rem;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border: 1.5px solid var(--rule);
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            color: var(--ink-soft);
            font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s var(--ease);
            white-space: nowrap;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
        }

        .home-btn svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; transition: transform 0.2s var(--ease); }
        .home-btn:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(99,102,241,0.15); }
        .home-btn:hover svg { transform: translateX(-2px); }

        /* ── HERO ── */
        .hero {
            padding: clamp(5rem, 10vw, 6.5rem) clamp(1.25rem, 5vw, 3rem) 0;
            max-width: 860px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            animation: fadeUp 0.6s var(--ease) both;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
            font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw, 3.25rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.1;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
            color: var(--ink);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .hero-meta {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .hero-date {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--ink-faint);
        }

        /* ── TABS ── */
        .tabs-wrap {
            max-width: 860px;
            margin: 2.5rem auto 0;
            padding: 0 clamp(1.25rem, 5vw, 3rem);
            animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.1s var(--ease) both;
        }

        .tabs {
            display: inline-flex;
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--rule);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 4px;
            gap: 2px;
        }

        .tab {
            padding: 0.5rem 1.125rem;
            border-radius: 7px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--ink-soft);
            font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.2s var(--ease);
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .tab:hover { color: var(--ink); }

        .tab.active {
            background: var(--accent);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(99,102,241,0.25);
        }

        /* ── DIVIDER ── */
        .divider {
            max-width: 860px;
            margin: 2.5rem auto 0;
            padding: 0 clamp(1.25rem, 5vw, 3rem);
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
        }

        /* ── CONTENT ── */
        .content {
            max-width: 860px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2.5rem clamp(1.25rem, 5vw, 3rem) 5rem;
        }

        /* Intro paragraph */
        .intro {
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
            color: var(--ink-soft);
            line-height: 1.75;
            padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
            animation: fadeUp 0.5s 0.05s var(--ease) both;
        }

        /* Section */
        .section {
            padding: 2.5rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
            animation: fadeUp 0.5s var(--ease) both;
        }

        .section:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

        .section-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: baseline;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .section-num {
            font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--ink-faint);
            width: 24px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .section h2 {
            font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.0625rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--ink);
            letter-spacing: -0.01em;
        }

        /* Items */
        .items {
            padding-left: 2.5rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0;
        }

        .item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 0.875rem;
            padding: 0.875rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
        }

        .item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

        .item-dot {
            width: 5px;
            height: 5px;
            background: var(--accent);
            border-radius: 50%;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            margin-top: 0.55rem;
            opacity: 0.6;
        }

        .item-text {
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: var(--ink-soft);
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        /* ── FOOTER ── */
        footer {
            border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
            background: var(--surface);
        }

        .footer-inner {
            max-width: 860px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem clamp(1.25rem, 5vw, 3rem);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 1rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .footer-brand {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--ink-faint);
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .footer-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.25rem;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .footer-links a {
            color: var(--ink-faint);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            transition: color 0.2s;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--ink); }

        /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
        @keyframes fadeUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); }
            to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .section:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.10s; }
        .section:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
        .section:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.20s; }
        .section:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.25s; }
        .section:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.30s; }

        /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .hero { padding: 4.5rem 1.25rem 0; }
            .hero h1 { font-size: 1.875rem; }
            .items { padding-left: 0.75rem; }
            .tabs-wrap { padding: 0 1.25rem; }
            .divider { margin: 2rem auto 0; }
            .content { padding: 2rem 1.25rem 4rem; }
            .section { padding: 2rem 0; }
            .section-header { gap: 0.75rem; }
            .item-text { font-size: 0.9rem; }
            .intro { font-size: 0.9rem; padding-bottom: 2rem; }

            .footer-inner {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 1rem;
                padding: 1.75rem 1.25rem;
            }
            .footer-links { gap: 1rem; }
        }

        @media (max-width: 400px) {
            .home-btn {
                top: 0.875rem;
                left: 0.875rem;
                font-size: 0.78rem;
                padding: 0.4rem 0.75rem;
            }

            .hero { padding: 4rem 1rem 0; }
            .hero h1 { font-size: 1.625rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
            .hero-date { font-size: 0.8rem; }

            .tabs-wrap { padding: 0 1rem; }
            .tabs { width: 100%; }
            .tab {
                flex: 1;
                text-align: center;
                font-size: 0.8rem;
                padding: 0.45rem 0.5rem;
            }

            .divider { margin: 1.75rem auto 0; }
            .content { padding: 1.75rem 1rem 3.5rem; }
            .intro { font-size: 0.85rem; padding-bottom: 1.75rem; }
            .section { padding: 1.75rem 0; }
            .section-header { gap: 0.625rem; margin-bottom: 1.125rem; }
            .section-num { font-size: 0.8rem; width: 20px; }
            .section h2 { font-size: 0.9375rem; }
            .items { padding-left: 0.5rem; }
            .item { gap: 0.625rem; padding: 0.75rem 0; }
            .item-dot { width: 4px; height: 4px; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
            .item-text { font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.65; }

            .footer-inner {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 1rem;
                padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
            }
            .footer-brand { font-size: 0.8rem; }
            .footer-links {
                gap: 0.75rem 1rem;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
            }
            .footer-links a { font-size: 0.8rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Fixed home button -->
    <a href="/" class="home-btn">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M19 12H5M12 5l-7 7 7 7"/>
        </svg>
        Back to Home
    </a>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="hero">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <div class="hero-meta">
            <span class="hero-date">Last updated: 04 Feb 2026</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Tabs -->
    <div class="tabs-wrap">
        <nav class="tabs">
            <a href="terms"   class="tab">Terms &amp; Conditions</a>
            <a href="privacy" class="tab active">Privacy Policy</a>
        </nav>
    </div>

    <hr class="divider">

    <!-- Main content -->
    <main class="content">

        <p class="intro">At UniSpace, we are committed to protecting your privacy and safeguarding your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your information when you use UniSpace — your personal digital vault.</p>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-header">
                <span class="section-num">01</span>
                <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="items">
                <div class="item"><span class="item-dot"></span><span class="item-text">Account information such as email address and basic profile details.</span></div>
                <div class="item"><span class="item-dot"></span><span class="item-text">Files uploaded by you, including documents, PDFs, images, and other supported formats.</span></div>
                <div class="item"><span class="item-dot"></span><span class="item-text">Limited technical information such as device type, browser, and IP address for security and performance purposes.</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-header">
                <span class="section-num">02</span>
                <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="items">
                <div class="item"><span class="item-dot"></span><span class="item-text">To create and manage your UniSpace account.</span></div>
                <div class="item"><span class="item-dot"></span><span class="item-text">To securely store, retrieve, and manage your uploaded files.</span></div>
                <div class="item"><span class="item-dot"></span><span class="item-text">To maintain platform security, prevent unauthorized access, and improve service reliability.</span></div>
                <div class="item"><span class="item-dot"></span><span class="item-text">To communicate important service-related updates when necessary.</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-header">
                <span class="section-num">03</span>
                <h2>File Privacy &amp; Ownership</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="items">
                <div class="item"><span class="item-dot"></span><span class="item-text">All files uploaded to UniSpace are private by default.</span></div>
                <div class="item"><span class="item-dot"></span><span class="item-text">Only authenticated users can access their own files.</span></div>
                <div class="item"><span class="item-dot"></span><span class="item-text">UniSpace does not view, analyze, sell, or share user files.</span></div>
                <div class="item"><span class="item-dot"></span><span class="item-text">You retain full ownership and control over all content you upload.</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-header">
                <span class="section-num">04</span>
                <h2>Data Storage &amp; Security</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="items">
                <div class="item"><span class="item-dot"></span><span class="item-text">User data is protected using authentication-based access controls.</span></div>
                <div class="item"><span class="item-dot"></span><span class="item-text">We follow industry-standard security practices to protect stored information.</span></div>
                <div class="item"><span class="item-dot"></span><span class="item-text">While we strive to protect your data, no online system can guarantee absolute security.</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-header">
                <span class="section-num">05</span>
                <h2>Your Rights &amp; Choices</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="items">
                <div class="item"><span class="item-dot"></span><span class="item-text">You can access, update, or delete your account information at any time.</span></div>
                <div class="item"><span class="item-dot"></span><span class="item-text">You may delete your account, after which your stored data may be permanently removed.</span></div>
                <div class="item"><span class="item-dot"></span><span class="item-text">For privacy-related concerns or requests, you can contact us directly.</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <div class="footer-inner">
            <span class="footer-brand">© 2026 UniSpace</span>
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="contact">Contact</a>
                <a href="terms">Terms</a>
                <a href="privacy">Privacy</a>
                <a href="mailto:unispace013@gmail.com">unispace013@gmail.com</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>